      <title>德州仪器 (TI) 因乐观预测而实现 2020 年以来最大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/texas-instruments-gives-solid-forecast-in-sign-of-chip-comeback</link>
